							<h3 class="text-xl font-playfair text-yellow-400">Forge Your Legacy</h3>
							<p class="text-white text-md">Design unique cards with ancient runic powers and bring them to life.</p>
						</div>
					</div>


					<div class="bg-[#0A0B1E] rounded-3xl p-8 border border-yellow-400">
						<div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-4">
							<svg width="44" height="44" viewbox="0 0 44 44" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
